<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>Imgur Gallery</title><link>https://imgur.com</link><description>description</description><lastBuildDate>2022-02-09 16:59:32.999936</lastBuildDate><item><title>&quot;you act and talk white&quot;   &quot;you're such an oreo&quot;</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/ATFpFEb</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XiFqvsw.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It's ridiculous to automatically assume that someone is going to act a certain way because of their race. Black, Asian, and Hispanic people have been told they're not acting black or Asian or Latino "enough" when they don't speak the way they're expected to, or if they like certain hobbies. 

People form so many assumptions that someone cannot be the person he or she is based on things that are stereotypical of their race. They feel forced into a box. 
Someone's surroundings do not change their race. 

It needs to be said: race is not a personality trait. It also needs to be said that calling someone "pretty (or) handsome for a ______girl/ guy" is disrespectful, like this woman in the video pointed out

whose name is Kelly Stamps btw</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ATFpFEb</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[EnglightenMe]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>a hat story</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/iFbblWE</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/nCBwUQA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/iFbblWE</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[AkitakaL]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Cool stove, bro</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/OkNFyKN</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ud9GRs6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6OBOWDX.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/niywmqY.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0pSuBbB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/aQoBeZ1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CaOJIa5.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/e82TxGh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tjBPG8s.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/yOVjC98.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/OkNFyKN</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[minPD0309]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Those kids are amazing.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/ZMtBIjK</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/etTEdXq.jpg" style="max-wi