lery/GFJvdbv</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GIPSuoW.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Our local Humane Society found this little starved fella on the street with a female. They gave my wife a call after she offered to foster dogs for them. When we brought him home, he was nervous and sat in his prison issued bed with his blanket.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KdWG2yy.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It took about two days for him to realize he wouldn't be taken back to the kennel. He gradually began to relax as my wife and I showered him with love and affection.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/DZbhI1P.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>His "prison" name was Dice, but we decided to call him Luca.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3AIskwl.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Turns out he LOVES, LOVES, LOVES walks and that's how I bonded with him.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PVA9HHN.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Now we're pretty inseparable.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6VWq2Dj.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Luca even likes hanging out in my home office.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JhzRlin.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It's hard to imagine sending him onto another family. I don't think any of us could bear that separation.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CIBoVY4.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kKDLwtu.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>So we've decided to adopt Luca. It wasn't even a close call. And I have a new drinking buddy.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/GFJvdbv</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Adamarket]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>A-Maz-Ing</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/6hE0OYu</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/53XzP6R.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/6hE0OYu</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[deaddogsmuggler]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Bitch he better be joking *Maddy voice*</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/UURaEpV</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Rxr2jwM.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/UURaEpV</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[keiara2000]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Professional Photos of Frankie MacDonald Taken By Professional Photographer John Ratchford</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/hSz3auO</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0JlpVPj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>My Face and the Blue Sky</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ZrTGUpX.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Me Sitting on the Bleachers</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gTAkLsN.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Me By the Sun and Clouds</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9rBHIB6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Me on the Soccer Field</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/t1gPgjv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Me Standing Up on the Soccer Field</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LjRBevq.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Me on the Socc